<div class="section-header">
  <h2 class="header--title">My writing practice</h2>
</div>

<div class="layout-grid--duo spacer-b--s">
  <section class="writing-card--summary">
    <p>I teach a a yearly summer workshop called <a href="/writing/writing-is-design-workshop/">Writing = Design</a> at <em>UdK Berlin</em>. For <em>form design magazine</em>, I wrote a column about <a href="/writing/form-columns/">digital nostalgia</a>. I’ve been <a href="https://christowski.de/blog" target="_blank">blogging</a> since 2006, and sometimes, I even make <a href="https://frohmannverlag.de/collections/literatur/products/warum-heisst-es" target="_blank">books</a>.</p>
    <p>Writing is an integral part of design for me. And—once you took the leap—it can be fun!</p>
  </section>

  <section class="recent-posts">
    <div class="container--normal">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="header--title">Recently published</h2>
        <div class="header--meta">
          <a class="link--pill link--rss" href="{{ site.url }}/feed.xml">RSS</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <ul class="post-list">
        {% for post in collections.posts | limit(3) | reverse %}
          <li class="post-teaser">
            <a class="post-teaser--link" href="{{ post.url }}">
              <img class="post-teaser--thumb" src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.imageAlt }}">
              <div class="post-teaser--data">
                <div class="post-teaser--title">
                  <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
                  <p>{{ post.data.abstract }}</p>
                </div>
                {# <time class="post-teaser--date">{{ post.data.date | dateFilter }}</time> #}
              </div>
            </a>
          </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
      <a class="button-arrow" href="/writing">All posts</a>
    <div>
  </section>

</div>
